{
  "texts": [
    "Our research shows that some threats considering the usage of AI exist, but at the same time, there is a broad range of possibilities, including combining plot lines, distinctive character development and high-quality artistic device conditioning.",
    "In an age when originality is hard to come by, utilizing AI instruments for writing inspiration seems promising.",
    "However, taking and processing the AI-generated results is all a human choice and responsibility.",
    "This leads us to the question of how roles are assigned in the joint work of machines and humans.",
    "According to Lee et al. (2022), the more writers got suggestions from GPT-3, the less they wrote and the less they felt ownership over the final texts."
  ]
}